This is the first release of ThereMaxi. [17/10/19]

There is no help available, and there are not much comments in the code, but it's easy to use.

It's all perl! Developed and tested with version 5.22.1

If your perl is not found under /usr/bin, you need to change the first line in ThereMaxi.pl
#!/path/to/perl -w

You may need to install some packages. ThereMaxi.pl will inform you about that on start.


*** Update [17/10/23]
- Worakround for locale-problem in numeric controllers.
- Better MIDI handling.
- Feature added: MidiFeedbackLoop - weird ;-)
  Use input from antennas to manipulate preset controllers.
- Fixed import routine.

*** Update [17/10/27]
- Fixed low/high note range
- 14bit support for controller input

*** Update [18/04/13]
- Fixed comma in numeric values
- Fixed some undefs
